Ext.data.JsonP['API_Builder_Tools_FAQ']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>API Builder Tools FAQ</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-50168642\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>API Builder Tools FAQ</h1>\n    <p>This document provides references to answer several API Builder Tools frequently asked questions (FAQs).    </p>\n    <p>    </p>\n<ul class=\"toc-indentation \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Tools_FAQ-section-src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-Submitabug\">Submit a bug</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Tools_FAQ-section-src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-SetupAppceleratorCLI\">Setup Appcelerator CLI</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Tools_FAQ-section-src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-CreateanAPIBuilderproject\">Create an API Builder project</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Tools_FAQ-section-src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-RunanAPIBuilderproject\">Run an API Builder project</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Tools_FAQ-section-src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-DeployanAPIBuilderproject\">Deploy an API Builder project</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Tools_FAQ-section-src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-Publishsourcecode\">Publish source code</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Tools_FAQ-section-src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-PublishsourcecodebyprovidingaDockerfile\">Publish source code by providing a Dockerfile</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Tools_FAQ-section-src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-PublishsourcecodeusinganexistingDockerfile\">Publish source code using an existing Dockerfile</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Tools_FAQ-section-src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-ConfigureaccesstotheAPIBuilderconsole\">Configure access to the API Builder console</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Tools_FAQ-section-src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-CreateamodelusingtheAPIBuilderconsole\">Create a model using the API Builder console</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Tools_FAQ-section-src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-BrandapublicAPI\">Brand a public API</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Tools_FAQ-section-src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-AddaSwaggerinterfacetoanAPI\">Add a Swagger interface to an API</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Tools_FAQ-section-src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-Customizethebuilt-inJSONformatter\">Customize the built-in JSON formatter</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Tools_FAQ-section-src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-AddanewJSONformattype\">Add a new JSON format type</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Tools_FAQ-section-src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-CreateAPIBuilderwebinterfaces\">Create API Builder web interfaces</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Tools_FAQ-section-src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-CreateandconfigureAPIBuilderprojects\">Create and configure API Builder projects</a>    </p>\n</li></ul>    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-Submitabug\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Submit a bug</span></h2>\n    <p>Refer to <a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Reporting_Bugs_or_Requesting_Features\">Reporting Bugs or Requesting Features</a> for more information.    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-SetupAppceleratorCLI\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Setup Appcelerator CLI</span></h2>\n    <p>Refer to the <i class=\" \">Setup</i> section of <a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_CLI\">API Builder CLI</a> for more information or to the Setup section of <a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Getting_Started\">API Builder Getting Started</a> for more information.    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-CreateanAPIBuilderproject\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Create an API Builder project</span></h2>\n    <p>Refer to the <i class=\" \">Create a project</i> section of <a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Getting_Started\">API Builder Getting Started</a> for more information.    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-RunanAPIBuilderproject\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Run an API Builder project</span></h2>\n    <p>Refer to the <i class=\" \">Run the project</i> section of <a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Getting_Started\">API Builder Getting Started</a> for more information.    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-DeployanAPIBuilderproject\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Deploy an API Builder project</span></h2>\n    <p>Refer to the <i class=\" \">Deploy the project</i> section of <a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Getting_Started\">API Builder Getting Started</a> for more information.    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-Publishsourcecode\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Publish source code</span></h2>\n    <p>Refer to the <i class=\" \">Publish source code</i> section of <a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_CLI\">API Builder CLI</a> for information on publishing source code using the legacy method.    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-PublishsourcecodebyprovidingaDockerfile\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Publish source code by providing a Dockerfile</span></h2>\n    <p>Refer to the <i class=\" \">Publish by providing </i>Dockerfile section of <a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_CLI\">API Builder CLI</a> for more information.    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-PublishsourcecodeusinganexistingDockerfile\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Publish source code using an existing Dockerfile</span></h2>\n    <p>Refer to the Publish by using existing Docker image section of <a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_CLI\">API Builder CLI</a> for more information.    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-ConfigureaccesstotheAPIBuilderconsole\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Configure access to the API Builder console</span></h2>\n    <p>Refer to the <i class=\" \">Configuration</i> section of <a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Console\">API Builder Console</a> for more information.    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-CreateamodelusingtheAPIBuilderconsole\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Create a model using the API Builder console</span></h2>\n    <p>Refer to the <i class=\" \">Create a new model</i> section of <a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Getting_Started\">API Builder Getting Started</a> and the <i class=\" \">Build</i> section of <a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Console\">API Builder Console</a> for more information.    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-BrandapublicAPI\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Brand a public API</span></h2>\n    <p>Refer to the <i class=\" \">Insert custom JavaScript and CSS</i> section of <a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Docs\">API Builder Docs</a> for more information.    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-AddaSwaggerinterfacetoanAPI\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Add a Swagger interface to an API</span></h2>\n    <p>Refer to the <i class=\" \">Swagger interface</i> section of <a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Docs\">API Builder Docs</a> for more information.    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-Customizethebuilt-inJSONformatter\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Customize the built-in JSON formatter</span></h2>\n    <p>Refer to the <i class=\" \">Customizing the built-in JSON formatter</i> section of <a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Formatters\">API Builder Formatters</a> for more information.    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-AddanewJSONformattype\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Add a new JSON format type</span></h2>\n    <p>Refer to the <i class=\" \">Adding a new format type</i> section of <a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Formatters\">API Builder Formatters</a> for more information.    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-CreateAPIBuilderwebinterfaces\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Create API Builder web interfaces</span></h2>\n    <p>Refer to <a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Web\">API Builder Web</a> for more information.    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-50168642_APIBuilderToolsFAQ-CreateandconfigureAPIBuilderprojects\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Create and configure API Builder projects</span></h2>\n    <p>To create and configure API Builder projects, including models and flows, refer to <a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Tools_Project\">API Builder Tools Project</a>.    </p>\n    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=50168642\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"API Builder Tools FAQ"});